snippet.title: Free Title Update 3 - Monster Hunter Rise: Sunbreak
snippet.description:
Prepare to jump headfirst into the chaos with the brave denizens of Kamura and Elgado. Chaotic Gore Magala and two Risen Elder Dragons headline a host of additions coming in Sunbreak Free Title Update, available Nov. 24!

Monster Hunter Rise: Sunbreak is available now on Nintendo Switch and PC / Steam!
https://www.monsterhunter.com/rise-sunbreak/en-us/

Start your journey today in Monster Hunter Rise, available now!
Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/monster-hunter-rise-plus-sunbreak-switch/
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1446780/MONSTER_HUNTER_RISE/
